name: The EpilepsiaAI Project #0017 (Special Edition)
description:
Last night I had a seizure, and my computer made some art in response.

-----------

An AI-generated collection about my battle with epilepsy and seizures using text-to-image AI models.

See failoften.net for more information on the project.

-----------

Size: 400x192
Format: MP4

-----------

Special Edition for 200+ Twitter Followers on @failoften

One of my earliest prototypes for creating a story interpreted by AI into video. 
Goes through states of being awake, in seizure, confusion, and the exhausting IRL loop that occurs.

<3
